  <name>OpenCut</name>
  <summary>Local-first video automation backend for Premiere Pro</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      OpenCut runs a local Flask backend for video editing automation,
      captioning, delivery checks, review bundles, and optional AI-assisted
      post-production workflows.
    </p>
    <p>
      The Linux package starts the OpenCut server on localhost so Premiere
      panels, MCP clients, and command-line workflows can connect without a
      cloud account.
    </p>
  </description>
